{"tid":2497931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我人生係咪玩完 失眠左成晚 你問我盡答","createTime":"2021-04-20T23:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T11:17:36.000Z","uid":337808,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fd079392cfd41e51c54c1fc8e02f19c0be8a969e","tid":2497931,"uid":337808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:40:54.000Z","msg":"細細個就有情緒病 大個左好似好返啲 <br />\n可以過返啲正常生活 有自己嘅目標<br />\n點知發夢比人咬左 依家仲排緊期分分鐘排到2023<br />\n日日都比呢單野纏繞住 情緒病又再復發過<br />\n晚晚失眠 覺得我幾努力都無將來 我人生係咪玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚失眠到依家 開個你問我答 真係你問咩我都盡答 睇吓答答吓會唔會有睡意<br />\n案情問題唔答太多 會自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6230f89ac0b949b064448b284754ecff845112","tid":2497931,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:43:16.000Z","msg":"你係咪預咗入去？大約幾耐？"},{"pid":"f5d42b8e4008b624962e82a5b37263b74242d083","tid":2497931,"uid":106051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:46:42.000Z","msg":"共勉之"},{"pid":"1e3182efbd3ed55c922a4ffa0bb83f6d9b33c115","tid":2497931,"uid":337808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc6230f89ac0b949b064448b284754ecff845112","tid":2497931,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:43:16.000Z","msg":"你係咪預咗入去？大約幾耐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:49:52.000Z","msg":"其實無話預左入去 但點都要有心理準備<br />\n入幾耐呢樣野近排有案例4年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dbc14df6ef62207a8cb89c1e86c47de0b1711e","tid":2497931,"uid":337808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d42b8e4008b624962e82a5b37263b74242d083","tid":2497931,"uid":106051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:46:42.000Z","msg":"共勉之"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:50:14.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0e4243a3eb3621ff25d5b25f4421ad41491615","tid":2497931,"